Dynasonics Temporary Lead Time Extension | April 16, 2014
Confidential & Proprietary
Dear Dynasonics Representative:
Recent sales volumes for TFX Ultra units have exceeded our expectations and have impacted our on-hand component inventory. Due to this unforeseen circumstance, we are temporarily extending the lead time for all TFX Ultra meters and for TFXL meters with Display Option 2.
Effective immediately, the extended lead time is six (6) weeks. However, as our component inventory is replenished, we will begin to ship orders as quickly as possible. We anticipate returning to normal lead times by the end of June.
Early visibility of increased demand helps ensure on-time deliveries. In order to help us proactively adjust our manufacturing forecast and avoid component shortages in the future, please be sure to notify your Badger Meter sales manager of any out-of-the-ordinary increases in quote and/or sales activity.
We will provide regular updates as we strive to return to normal lead times. Please contact your Badger Meter customer service representative regarding any projects with critical timelines.
Regards,
BADGER METER, INC.
Cheryl Ades Anspach Marketing Manager
